A.6 Collapse Point Proof

Solve P_eff = 0:

```
P_node - Ï‰Â·N^(1/3) = 0
N^(1/3) = P_node/Ï‰
N = (P_node/Ï‰)Â³
```

Thus for N > (P_node/Ï‰)Â³, P_eff < 0, meaning coordination overhead exceeds available compute capacity.

A.7 Locality-Aware Extension

Let â„“ be the fraction of tasks solvable within k hops. Then:

```
